en.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String/substr\"><code>String.prototype.substr()</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String/slice\"><code>String.prototype.slice()</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Definition","id":"summary"},{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Beschreibung","id":"description"},{"text":"Beispiele","id":"examples"},{"text":"Spezifikationen","id":"spezifikationen"},{"text":"Browser Kompatibilität","id":"browser_kompatibilität"},{"text":"Siehe auch","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"Die substring() Methode gibt einen Teilstring eines Strings zwischen einem Index und einem anderen, oder dem Ende der Zeichenkette zurück.","popularity":0.002,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"String.prototype.substring()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"String.prototype.substring()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"String.prototype.substring()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"String.prototype.substring()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"String.prototype.substring()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"String.prototype.substring()","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"String.prototype.substring()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"String.prototype.substring()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"String.prototype.substring()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/string/substring","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/string/substring/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript","title":"JavaScript"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference","title":"JavaScript-Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects","title":"Globale Objekte"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String","title":"String"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String/substring","title":"String.prototype.substring()"}],"pageTitle":"String.prototype.substring() - JavaScript | MDN","noIndexing":false}}